{"tid":1301114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[放榜] 想搞tg group 分享下學科同就業出路","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:28:14.000Z","uid":253300,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7d823dd538e0b1d331fe07d097d6687d203c6f","tid":1301114,"uid":253300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"近日見到年青人為香港出心出力 相信有部分前線既年青人係今屆dse考生 回想起當年放榜時 好多野都唔識 導致揀錯科 行左冤枉路 相信好多人都有咁既經驗 我亦係其中一個 趁今次我想略盡棉力...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望能夠集結咁多位行業既知識幫助放榜生 令佢地唔好步我地後塵 <br />\n<br />\n想以下面既分類開tg group<br />\n<strong>現時idea:<br />\n1. 以工種分類<br />\n2. 以行業分類<br />\n3. 以學科分類（夠多人既話）</strong><br />\n<br />\n有冇手足有興趣一齊搞 報一報可以係邊個範疇幫下手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當日年輕人企係我地前面 依家我地要做佢地既後盾同智囊團</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我愛香港</span>"},{"pid":"3c9d6dcf3b063dd36d32fbc858aac3b07d30096e","tid":1301114,"uid":253300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:22:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8300c35513de2c7824a06cf3698b3cae2ba16979","tid":1301114,"uid":253300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:22:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dfea765e21badbce43017f85a3642047714b05b3","tid":1301114,"uid":253300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d4c9561ea8dbf28e1d5062c4275eb5704bd52fd8","tid":1301114,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n工種方面可以比到d資訊大家參考下"},{"pid":"7bac8fc6b07d7b247a0b2d180a5638b8d3b7215c","tid":1301114,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"唔好做it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e6452a352c086f399914822cec16ff18e8abe1","tid":1301114,"uid":253300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20